{"surah":108,"ayahs":[{"ayah":1,"arabic":"إِنَّآ أَعۡطَيۡنَٰكَ ٱلۡكَوۡثَرَ","translation":"Indeed, We have granted you, [O Muhammad], al-Kawthar","transliteration":"Inna aAAtaynaka alkawthara","juz":30,"wordCount":3},{"ayah":2,"arabic":"فَصَلِّ لِرَبِّكَ وَٱنۡحَرۡ","translation":"So pray to your Lord and sacrifice [to Him alone]","transliteration":"Fasalli lirabbika wainhar","juz":30,"wordCount":3},{"ayah":3,"arabic":"إِنَّ شَانِئَكَ هُوَ ٱلۡأَبۡتَرُ","translation":"Indeed, your enemy is the one cut off","transliteration":"Inna shaniaka huwa alabtaru","juz":30,"wordCount":4}]}